segment.source: Microsoft Edge requirements and language support
Microsoft Edge is pre-installed on all Windows 10-capable devices that meet the minimum system requirements and are on the supported language list.
Some of the components in this table might also need additional system resources.
Check the component's documentation for more information.
Windows 10 (32-bit or 64-bit) Windows 10 Mobile Note: For specific Windows 10 Mobile requirements, see the Minimum hardware requirements for Windows 10 Mobile topic.
DVD-ROM drive (if installing from a DVD-ROM)
Super VGA (800 x 600) or higher-resolution monitor with 256 colors
Microsoft DirectX 9 or later with Windows Display Driver Model (WDDM) 1.0 driver
Internet connection and a compatible pointing device
